Verification and documentation for making updates to records for the author, book, publisher, student, and verified_member models
BOOK MODEL
Description: Update a book record
Endpoint: http://localhost:3002/api/v1/book/update-book/id/:id
Method: PUT
Params: id - 1
Request Payload:
{
"price": "$300.00"
	
}



RESPONSE
{
    "message": "Success",
    "resp": {
        "data": {
            "id": 1,
            "title": "Business Statistics In Practice",
