AUTHOR MODEL
Description: Update an author record
Endpoint: http://localhost:3002/api/v1/author/update-author/id/:id
Method: PUT
Params: id - 1
Request Payload:
{
"name": "Odam"
	
}

RESPONSE
{
    "message": "Success",
    "resp": {
        "data": {
            "id": 1,
            "author": "Lammle",
