Description: Update a student record
Endpoint: http://localhost:3002/api/v1/student/update-student/id/:id
Method: PUT
Params: id - 1
Request Payload:
{
	"university": "UCLA",
"street": "1419 Westwood Blvd",
"city": "Los Angeles",
"zipcode": "90002"

	
}

